### Step it up towards a healthier you in 2021
The One Million Step Challenge 2020 was the most incredible event to date. And
this year's will be even bigger and better, so register your interest to be
Walk them. Jog them. Dance them. However you choose to move, take at least
10,000 steps a day for three months and you’ll reach your million.
You can take on the challenge alone, or do it as a team. Either way, join the
huge online community of steppers that will help you stride with confidence
towards your goals. You’ll get regular emails to keep you motivated and we’ll
support you with great ideas and mini-challenges to keep you on track.
**You do one million sponsored steps. We transform lives. Together, we end the
